author: Rick Coleman
title: MVC Cross Country Super Meet
text:
MVC Cross Country Super Meet Posted: Follow @KWWLSports 
The Mississippi Valley Conference boys and girls super meet held at Irv Warren Golf course in Waterloo. 12-hundred runners competed in the event. In the girls race Mary Arch led from wire to wire to take the MVC championship. And in the boys race Tyson Vandraska of Cedar Rapids Prairie is first while Cedar Falls Sam Schillinger and Issac Smith finished second and third to help the Tigers win the team trophy.
